story.text: My throat feels like I am going to get strep again? So odd. Totally gone yesterday. Today, back in full force. Perhaps an allergic reaction to one of the new supplements?

Lots of things happening today - about to depart for the next two weeks on Sunday - so much to do before them. Leaving for NY bar swearing in ceremony, then John and Kelsey Wedding. Very exciting stuff.
